lead_paragraph: Denmark's Kevin Magnussen will race for Haas next season in place of Mexican Esteban Gutierrez, the U.S.-owned Formula One team announced on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Haas F1 Drop Gutierrez and Sign Magnussen
headline.main: Haas F1 Drop Gutierrez and Sign Magnussen
